    <summary>Four-phase influencer framework: discover micro-influencers (10K–100K) by engagement quality, vet for audience match and fraud signals, personalized outreach, FTC-compliant disclosures, track ROI.</summary>
    <tags>
      <tag>influencer-marketing</tag>
      <tag>creator-partnerships</tag>
      <tag>growth</tag>
      <tag>micro-influencers</tag>
